    Black Aracnia emerged from the tank, as did Paralysis. Together they 
entered the bridge to find Atma and his patner playing with themselfs.
    "You two, go and guard our new little addition to the family, Tarantulas. 
And the Maximals too." she ordered, taking her place at the command station. 
"Paralysis, tell Quickstrike to come here. I have a mission for him. I want 
him, Venomus, and Solo to go to a disclosed location and retrive...well, I'll 
have to tell him when he gets here with the others. Atma and Pursuedo will 
remain here with the rest of us in case of attack, but Aerostreak, Grappler, 
and Guantix will be dispatched if aid is needed." She said.
